content.p: As a returning student you must register with the University at the beginning of each academic session. You are required to complete online registration only. Online registration will open for the majority of returning students at the beginning of September. You will receive an email to your University email account informing you when online registration has opened for you. Term times, exam dates and other key dates for the academic year. All international students undertaking full-time studies in Malaysia are required to obtain a Student Pass (Visa). Access support for your health and wellbeing, talk to someone about your concerns and look after your health. The University of Nottingham Malaysia Campus Jalan Broga, 43500 Semenyih Selangor Darul Ehsan Malaysia telephone: +6 (03) 8924 8663 email: student_registry@nottingham.edu.my
